data.description: Contract Pending. Step into this charming home, boasting great curb appeal & situated on an expansive lot within an established neighborhood. The enchanting mid-century design features exposed beams and large Pella windows. Upon entry, the welcoming living room and formal dining area greet you offering a perfect setting for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories. The kitchen presents the option to maintain its cozy layout or seamlessly expand into the adjacent hearth room with seamless access to the patio and large, fenced-in yard.  Rounding out the main floor are 3 comfortable bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, one being an ensuite off the primary bedroom. Venture downstairs to the basement where a family room and 4th bedroom await. New windows and drain tile mean the new owner can focus on selecting their finishes to make the space perfectly theirs. A generously sized laundry room and two storage rooms ensure ample space for organization and practicality.
